41
00:05:27,490 --> 00:05:30,220
SPEAKER_15: Master Fugui is going home. You take him.

130
00:14:07,740 --> 00:14:10,330
SPEAKER_15: The game's not over yet!

140
00:14:44,779 --> 00:14:47,769
SPEAKER_15: I am very sorry, but you've got nothing left.

141
00:14:48,049 --> 00:14:51,779
SPEAKER_15: What could you stake the bet on?
We don't accept empty bets.

146
00:15:03,730 --> 00:15:06,529
SPEAKER_15: We'll formalize the transfer in a few days...

147
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:08,289
SPEAKER_15: and explain to your old man.

163
00:17:30,210 --> 00:17:32,400
SPEAKER_15: Mr. Xu, any mistakes?

289
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:45,220
SPEAKER_15: The wounded who froze to death.

301
00:33:58,930 --> 00:34:00,589
SPEAKER_15: They've all run off.

302
00:34:00,660 --> 00:34:02,130
SPEAKER_15: How could that be?

313
00:34:31,230 --> 00:34:32,460
SPEAKER_15: So, no running?

569
01:05:52,960 --> 01:05:55,360
SPEAKER_15: Youqing, is that tea for me?

639
01:13:56,729 --> 01:13:58,420
SPEAKER_15: Fugui, listen to me.

640
01:13:58,489 --> 01:14:02,430
SPEAKER_15: We have to try and bear it,
even in the worst of times.

709
01:21:26,710 --> 01:21:28,470
SPEAKER_15: Who the heck is she?

710
01:21:29,310 --> 01:21:31,279
SPEAKER_15: Let her go!

820
01:31:29,710 --> 01:31:32,510
SPEAKER_15: You're just in time. We've just finished.

822
01:31:36,520 --> 01:31:38,449
SPEAKER_15: We must be going.

863
01:36:16,430 --> 01:36:17,989
SPEAKER_15: Chairman Mao...

864
01:36:18,869 --> 01:36:21,600
SPEAKER_15: Comrade Fengxia's mine now.

906
01:40:35,890 --> 01:40:37,409
SPEAKER_15: I'll make something.

907
01:40:37,489 --> 01:40:40,220
SPEAKER_15: Lunch is all taken care of.

934
01:42:41,649 --> 01:42:43,579
SPEAKER_15: I had the photo framed.

1042
01:50:52,210 --> 01:50:54,829
SPEAKER_15: Do as Mommy says and push.

1043
01:50:54,909 --> 01:50:56,640
SPEAKER_15: Everything will be fine.

1074
01:53:13,180 --> 01:53:14,939
SPEAKER_15: Wang Bin! Stand up!

1075
01:53:19,020 --> 01:53:22,050
SPEAKER_15: This is the same Wang Bin
who once insulted...

1078
01:53:31,029 --> 01:53:33,159
SPEAKER_15: We dragged him here today...

1079
01:53:33,300 --> 01:53:36,270
SPEAKER_15: to educate him, to criticize him...

1080
01:53:37,340 --> 01:53:39,899
SPEAKER_15: and to let him witness her giving birth.

1081
01:53:39,970 --> 01:53:42,909
SPEAKER_15: To show him the heirs
of this new, Red world.

1149
01:59:09,670 --> 01:59:11,329
SPEAKER_15: Are they in there?

1160
01:59:40,970 --> 01:59:43,159
SPEAKER_15: 7.9 pounds is excellent.

1161
01:59:43,239 --> 01:59:45,760
SPEAKER_15: If you get a car from the factory...

1233
02:05:53,369 --> 02:05:55,399
SPEAKER_15: Careful! Don't drop them!

